&lt;p&gt;The Project Manager will support Coegi in the organization and internal management of high-touch accounts. As an expert in project management, this role is responsible for management of processes, systems, documents, timelines, assets, and relationships pertaining to individual accounts. This person will be a key counterpart to our Account Strategy Directors, providing detail-level knowledge to complement their partner and strategic knowledge. The Project Manager will also support Account Managers and Operations by managing deliverables, keeping production and asset trackers up to date, leading billing and budget actualization, and overall keeping account teams on track.&lt;/p&gt;
