&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Coegi&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Coegi is an independent, full-service digital media agency operating across North America under the Meet the People network, alongside sister companies True Media and RADaR Analytics. We partner with brands to plan, activate, and measure media in a way that prizes transparency, collaboration, and outcomes our clients can appreciate and understand. Our independence is a feature, not a footnote - it lets us choose the right partners for each client rather than the ones a holding company tells us to use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Programmatic Specialist is a hands-on trader and the day-to-day owner of campaign execution across Coegi&#39;s programmatic book of business. You will build, traffic, QA, and optimize campaigns across display, video, CTV, audio, and emerging channels - primarily in The Trade Desk - while working closely with strategy, client engagement, and measurement teams to keep performance on track. This is the craft role at the heart of our operations: the work you do every day is the difference between a campaign that delivers and one that doesn&#39;t.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
