&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and traffic programmatic campaigns across display, video, CTV, audio, native, and other channels - primarily in The Trade Desk, with additional DSPs as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate media plans into clean, well-structured campaign architectures: line items, audiences, frequency, dayparting, geo, and creative assignments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;QA every campaign before launch - pixels and tracking firing, creative specs correct, deal IDs active, audiences attached, budgets and flight dates accurate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and maintain Coegi&#39;s standards for brand safety, inventory quality, MFA exclusion, and viewability across every campaign you touch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document setup decisions and naming conventions so anyone on the team can pick up the campaign and understand what&#39;s happening.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Day-to-Day Optimization &amp;amp; Pacing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
