&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Timelines &amp;amp; Task Management: &lt;/strong&gt;Develop efficient processes for high-touch accounts that allow the team to meet internal and external goals. Apply advanced problem-solving to anticipate risks, unblock teams, and proactively restructure timelines when milestones are threatened.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Asset, Asana &amp;amp; Communication Management: &lt;/strong&gt;Own end-to-end management of account documents, URLs, copy, creative, and collateral. Maintain Asana as the single source of truth for assigned accounts, translating action items into assignments and keeping teams unified across email, Slack, and meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Billing, Budget &amp;amp; Contract Oversight: &lt;/strong&gt;Complete monthly billing for assigned clients and manage rollover underspend/overspend. Take a lead role in managing contracts and scope-of-work outlines with external parties, including vendors and clients, escalating contract risk to the Supervisor.&lt;/li&gt;
