&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Contribution: &lt;/strong&gt;Proactively identify opportunities to simplify or eliminate PMO processes and templates; bring forward documented recommendations to the Supervisor, with attention to what should be removed, not only what should be added. Support the department&#39;s project work as assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
